==後續==
光芒隊這場勝利帶領他們隊史第四度打入季後賽，晉級[[2013年美國聯盟外卡晉級賽|美聯外卡賽]]與{{le|2013年克里夫蘭印地安人隊球季|2013 Cleveland Indians season|克里夫蘭印地安人隊}}進行交戰，成功取勝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports-ak.espn.go.com/mlb/preview?id=331002105|title=Rays-Indians Preview|date=2013-10-02|work=ESPN|accessdate=2013-10-02|archive-date=2017-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170706092111/http://sports-ak.espn.go.com/mlb/preview?id=331002105|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://scores.espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=331002105|title=Alex Cobb guides Rays past Indians, into ALDS vs. Red Sox|date=2013-10-02|work=ESPN|accessdate=2013-10-03|archive-date=2016-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403092704/http://scores.espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=331002105|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Chastain|first=Bill|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2013_10_02_tbamlb_clemlb_1&mode=recap_away&c_id=tb|title=Famous Rays deliver, topping Tribe in Wild Card|date=2013-10-02|work=MLB.com|accessdate=2013-10-03|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232834/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2013_10_02_tbamlb_clemlb_1&mode=recap_away&c_id=tb|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但隨後在[[2013年美國聯盟分區賽|美聯分區賽]]中以一勝三敗的戰績輸給當年度的世界冠軍{{le|2013年波士頓紅襪隊球季|2013 Boston Red Sox season|波士頓紅襪隊}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2013/matchup/_/teams/rays-redsox|title=Rays v Red Sox|date=2013-10-02|work=ESPN|accessdate=2013-10-03|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304105042/http://espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2013/matchup/_/teams/rays-redsox|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

這場比賽的紀錄也算入正規賽季的[[棒球統計|棒球統計]]中，舉例來說，[[埃文·朗歌利亞|埃文·朗歌利亞]]三局上半的那支全壘打打破[[斯坦·穆休|斯坦·穆休]]所創下的賽季最後一場比賽所打出之全壘打的紀錄，將紀錄推進到7支<ref name="longorecord">{{cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/rays-evan-longoria-delivers-when-it-matters-most/c-62258510 |title=Longoria delivers when it matters most |last1=Gonzalez |first1=Alden |date=2013-10-01 |publisher=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |accessdate=2013-10-02}}</ref>。他單場四個打數三支安打，其中有一支二壘安打、一支全壘打及兩分[[打點|打點]]。這讓他在2009年至2013年間，在賽季最後一場比賽的成績是19個打數11支安打，含七支全壘打及十分打點<ref name="longorecord"/> <ref name="franchise">{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/TBD/ |title=Tampa Bay Rays Team History & Encyclopedia |work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]] |accessdate=2013-09-30 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5lgXtbJui?url=http://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/TBD/ |archivedate=2009-12-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

